<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,151,428]" pageId="4" pageNumber="450">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,295,320]" pageId="4" pageNumber="450">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Vilbaste, 1968" authorityName="Vilbaste" authorityYear="1968" box="[603,1042,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Arboridia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="450" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculifrons">
